Package: stegcore
Version: 3.0.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: The Malware Files <ops@themalwarefiles.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/elementmerc/Stegcore
Description: Crypto-steganography toolkit
 Stegcore combines encryption and steganography. It encrypts your
 payload and hides the ciphertext inside ordinary image or audio files.
 Features three AEAD ciphers (Ascon-128, ChaCha20-Poly1305, AES-256-GCM),
 deniable dual-payload mode, built-in steganalysis suite with five
 detectors, and both GUI and CLI interfaces.
 .
 Intended for journalists, activists, security researchers, and CTF players.
